title: Avada.Wordpress.Theme.v3.5.3-THEME-ONLY
description:
Name: Avada - Responsive Multi-Purpose Theme
Type: Wordpress Theme
Release Date: 29 July 14
Version: 3.5.3
Columns: 2
Compatible Browsers: IE8, IE9, IE10, IE11, Firefox, Safari, Opera, Chrome
Software Version: WordPress 3.9, 3.8, 3.7, 3.6, 3.5, 3.4, 3.3, 3.2
Compatible With: WPML, BuddyPress 1.9.x, WooCommerce 2.1.x, bbPress 2.5.x, Gravity Forms, Easy Digital Downloads, Events Calendar PRO, Events Calendar
Layout: Responsive
Files Included: PHP Files, CSS Files, JS Files
Widget Ready: Yes

Avada is the ultimate multi-purpose WordPress theme. It is so clean, super flexible and has a fully responsive design! This multi-purpose WordPress theme sets the new standard with endless possibilities. And its the most easy-to use theme on the market! Avada is very intuitive to use and completely ready to operate out of the box. Built with HTML5 & CSS3, a lot of thought and care went into this theme making it a pleasure to use.

This contains THEME FILES ONLY, meaning there is NO DOCUMENTATION, NO PSD FILES OR NOTHING ELSE EXTRA included. 

If you like it, please support the creators and buy it! This theme seriously Kick Ass!
